description.displayText: Tina is Amazing! She is not only caring and fun but is patient and dedicated. She worked with us for a little over a year and our son has grown into an incredible and well articulated toddler. We couldn't have been happier with her. We still rely on her when my parents aren't able to keep J while we work. I definitely recommend her to anyone looking in to hiring an experienced and caring babysitter.
